  "detailed_description": "The Wand Wizard is a rogue-like shoot 'em up based on classics from the flash era. At each level more enemies are spawned and you choose a skill card, creating combinations of power until the computer explodes (just kidding).<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469890/extras/51c818f36478aea54478dd63eac525a3.poster.avif?t=1689203762\" width=590 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469890/extras/51c818f36478aea54478dd63eac525a3.webm?t=1689203762\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469890/extras/51c818f36478aea54478dd63eac525a3.mp4?t=1689203762\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You start from scratch each round, use the right combinations to balance your battle. Using new capes and wands gives you extra benefits.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469890/extras/e475dc0fb3dabbd0aa6e77bbeeb5a488.poster.avif?t=1689203762\" width=590 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469890/extras/e475dc0fb3dabbd0aa6e77bbeeb5a488.webm?t=1689203762\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2469890/extras/e475dc0fb3dabbd0aa6e77bbeeb5a488.mp4?t=1689203762\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About the game and gameplay:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Several combinations of skills and items.</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Leaderboards system with Global rank.</li></ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>New wands, skills and capes to improve your combat.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_im